title: DEWA organises Excellence Camp for senior management (Dubai Electricity and Water Authority)
text: ( Source : Dubai Electricity and Water Authority ) Fri, 09 Oct 2015 Dubai Electricity and Water Authority (DEWA) has held an excellence camp for senior managers at the Grand Hyatt hotel in Dubai. The camp was attended by HE Saeed Mohammed Al
